e reimagining SaaS economics and simplifying complexity.\",\"type\":\"text\"}]}]},\"image_alignment\":\"bottom-right\",\"background_color\":{\"value\":\"#F4D6BB\",\"plugin\":\"storyblok-palette\"}}],\"title\":\"\",\"layout\":\"overflow\",\"component\":\"feature_card_carousel\"},{\"_uid\":\"8a437928-397d-4269-a569-ac74e75b2f50\",\"title\":\"Real stories from real customers\",\"hidden\":false,\"section\":[{\"id\":\"\",\"_uid\":\"4be6fc70-c0c9-40d9-8e09-2f15c82cfa06\",\"ctas\":[],\"layout\":\"default\",\"eyebrow\":\"\",\"component\":\"section_wrapper\",\"footer_text\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\"}]},\"section_title\":\"\",\"background_type\":\"\",\"heading_variant\":\"\",\"background_color\":\"\",\"section_subtitle\":\"\",\"heading_alignment\":\"\",\"section_title_size\":\"h2\",\"background_gradient\":\"\"}],\"component\":\"tabs\",\"subelements\":[{\"_uid\":\"a3f250c4-7a7e-4bcc-bc8c-2805b032fd56\",\"text\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"textAlign\":null},\"content\":[{\"text\":\"\\\"\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"textStyle\",\"attrs\":{\"color\":\"#000000\"}}]},{\"text\":\"This platform is about extracting more information, more connectivity, more value...things that our SREs are beating down the door for us to do. [The constant product evolution] has kept us really excited and we continue to be excited.\",\"type\":\"text\"},{\"text\":\"\\\"\",\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"textStyle\",\"attrs\":{\"color\":\"#000000\"}}]}]}]},\"type\":\"\",\"image\":{\"id\":137993293943313,\"alt\":\"\",\"name\":\"\",\"focus\":\"\",\"title\":\"\",\"source\":\"\",\"filename\":\"https://a-us.storyblok.com/f/1022730/726x726/4fb59e0a06/quote-blackrock.png\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"fieldtype\":\"asset\",\"meta_data\":{},\"is_external_url\":false},\"quote\":\"\",\"title\":\"BlackRock\",\"border\":false,\"component\":\"tab_element\",\"background\":\"\",\"media_type\":\"image\",\"bottom_text\":{\"type\":\"doc\",\